title: Youth unemployment rate in Saudi Arabia in 2019
summary: In general Youth unemployment rate has rose over the Year.
Youth unemployment rate is slightly increasing from 2012 to 2014.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2013 and 2014.
Maximum Youth unemployment rate, about 30.12 was reported at Year 2014
The lowest Youth unemployment rate, of value 27.84 was reported at Year 2012
